p: Subpoena Territory of Washington County of Lincoln}ss To C. F. Wandlon In the name of the United States, you are hereby required to appear before the undersigned, one of the Justices of the Peace in and for said County, on the 27th day of February 1885 at 4 o'clock P.M., at his office in Sprague W.T. to give evidence in a certain cause then and there to be tried between the Territory of Washington PLaintiff and E. Romick Defendant, on the part of the Territory Given under my hand this 27th day of February 1885 E.G. Pendleton justice of the Peace
